data.description:
Embark on a journey of untapped potential and breathtaking vistas with this hidden gem nestled in the heart of the West Valley, just outside Anaconda, Montana. Spanning .344 acres, this expansive property is a canvas awaiting the strokes of your imagination to craft the home of your dreams. Pass through the threshold into a spacious living area adorned with expansive windows, bathing the room in natural light and offering captivating shots of the surrounding landscape. Beyond lies a generous dining space, seamlessly connected to the fenced backyard through a sliding glass door, beckoning you to indulge in the blissful harmony of indoor/outdoor living.
Imagine yourself awakening to the awe-inspiring Mount Haggin, one of Montana's most iconic peaks, as you savor your morning brew on the covered back deck. The well-appointed kitchen stands ready to cater to your culinary desires, boasting ample counter and cabinet space, ideal for hosting memorable soirées.  Venture down the hall to discover three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and an upstairs laundry room, offering both comfort and convenience. Descend into the basement, where a second living area, a supplementary kitchenette, three additional bedrooms, a full bathroom, and an extra storage room await, providing boundless opportunities for expansion and personalization.  Outside, you'll also find a large, 2 car garage, providing ample parking and storage opportunities.
